    "abstract": "<jats:title>Summary</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  <jats:list list-type=\"bullet\">\n                    <jats:list-item>\n                      <jats:p>We use a data quality model to demonstrate that BCG vaccination is correlated with protection from death from COVID19</jats:p>\n                    </jats:list-item>\n                    <jats:list-item>\n                      <jats:p>From a mechanistic perspective, BCG is well described to elicit its protective non-specific effects through the process of trained immunity.</jats:p>\n                    </jats:list-item>\n                    <jats:list-item>\n                      <jats:p>Therapeutically enhancing trained immunity may therefore be an important mechanism in protection from the lethal effects of COVID19</jats:p>\n                    </jats:list-item>\n                  </jats:list>\n                </jats:p>",
